title: Yawhen Branavitski
text:
Yawhen Branavitski (; ; born 15 May 1981) is a retired <a href="Belarus">Belarus</a>ian professional <a href="Association%20football">football</a>er. His last club was <a href="FC%20Khimik%20Svetlogorsk">Khimik Svetlogorsk</a>.
Career.
Born in <a href="Soligorsk">Soligorsk</a>, Branavitski began playing football in FC RUOR Minsk's youth system. He joined <a href="FC%20Shakhtyor%20Soligorsk">FC Shakhtyor Soligorsk</a>'s senior team and made his <a href="Belarusian%20Premier%20League">Belarusian Premier League</a> debut in 2001.
